              },
              "free_text": [
                " 87 m curved neutron guide of the",
                " high flux reactor. Flux of 6.E+8 n/cm**2/sec,",
                " cadmium ratio of 1.E+6, gamma flux reduced by a",
                " factor of 1.E+6."
